---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Footer from "../layouts/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="About - Annotation Cache">
    <main>
        <h2>Project</h2>
        <p>
            Annotation Cache is a public <a href="https://registry.opendata.aws/">AWS Open Data</a>
            resource providing pre-built <a href="https://pcingola.github.io/SnpEff/">SnpEff</a> and
            <a href="https://www.ensembl.org/info/docs/tools/vep/index.html">VEP</a> annotation
            caches for the <a href="https://nf-co.re/">nf-core</a> community. Created with
            <a href="https://www.nextflow.io/">Nextflow</a> and
            <a href="https://cloud.seqera.io/">Seqera Platform</a>, it eliminates the need for
            each user to download large annotation databases individually.
        </p>

        <h2>Contributors</h2>
        <ul class="contributors">
            <li>
                <a href="https://github.com/maxulysse">Maxime U. Garcia</a>
                &mdash; creator and maintainer
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="https://github.com/matthdsm">Matthias De Smet</a>
                &mdash; contributor
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Nextflow Summit 2023 &mdash; Barcelona</h2>
        <p>
            Maxime Garcia presented <em>"Annotation cache: using nf-core/modules and Seqera Platform to
            build an AWS open data resource"</em> at the
            <a href="https://summit.nextflow.io/2023/barcelona/">Nextflow Summit 2023</a> in Barcelona.
        </p>
        <p>
            The talk described the journey of building this public resource using nf-core/modules,
            orchestrating workflows with Nextflow, deploying via Seqera Platform, and publishing
            the data on AWS Open Data.
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>Event:</strong> Nextflow Summit 2023, Barcelona
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Date:</strong> October 19, 2023
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Location:</strong> Torre Glòries, Barcelona
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Watch:</strong>
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPZ8WHdZGxmUotnP-tWRVNtuNWpN7xbpL">
                    Nextflow Summit 2023 playlist
                </a>
            </li>
        </ul>

        <Footer />
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    h2 {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        color: rgb(var(--accent-dark));
    }
    .contributors {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
    }
    .contributors li {
        padding: 0.5rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 40%);
    }
    .contributors li:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
    }
</style>
